Story: Fixed Line Sanity
Meta:
@tag tag:admin,tag:application,version:Release-02,version:Sprint-01.02

Narrative:
  As a user
  I should be able to create FL orders
  
Scenario:AnkitaFLNP006 -Consumer,Vodafone Superfast Fibre Plus and Home Phone, SPAREPAIR   
Meta:@AnkitaFLNP006
@FolderName AnkitaFLNP006
@Ankita
Given Place screenshots in Folder 'FolderName'
Given Login with 'QP' in 'Env'
When Create the account type 'PostpaidConsumerzzyy'
And Create New 'NewPostpaid' and Perform 'AboutRecordOfMenuItem' with About Record
And Perform 'RunQueryOfMenuItem' and Execute query 'Tokenization'
And Update Contact Number 'ContactNumber'
And Create New Premise 'SPAREPAIRCBU'
And Filter Promotion 'SPAREPAIRLine and Fibre with Speed 38|FTR5*&&Existing mobile customer'
When Get the Router Number
And Update ICCID against 'EnterRouterNoinVodafBroadbRouter'
And Reserve Order
And Perform Credit Vet
And Make payment with 'ONAccountNon-CardPopNO'
And Submit the Order 'NormalSubmitFL'


